Package: cograph
Title: Modern Network Visualization for R
Version: 1.5.2
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mohammed", "Saqr", role = "aut"),
    person("Sonsoles", "L\u00f3pez-Pernas", 
           email = "sonsoles.lopez@uef.fi", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Santtu", "Tikka", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Provides high-quality static and interactive network plots. As a
    modern, extensible network visualization package, `cograph` accepts adjacency
    matrices, edge lists, or igraph objects and offers customizable layouts,
    node shapes, edge styles, and themes. Designed for publication-ready
    visualizations with a pipe-friendly API.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: http://sonsoles.me/cograph/
